433
00:29:29.640 --> 00:29:30.932
Magandang ideya, tama ba?

434
00:29:31.535 --> 00:29:34.580
Pumayag ka ba talaga?

435
00:29:34.580 --> 00:29:36.940
Ngayon ikaw ay umiibig,

436
00:29:36.940 --> 00:29:39.294
