Kung okay lang sayo...

444
00:30:31.693 --> 00:30:34.365
Isa na naman ba itong dad tantrum?

445
00:30:34.365 --> 00:30:37.365
Baby ba ito o ano?

446
00:30:37.365 --> 00:30:40.302
Isang salita pa, at tatahiin ko ang iyong bibig.

447
00:30:47.434 --> 00:30:49.277
